import seaborn as sns
import matplotlib.ticker as ticker
def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    plt.figure(figsize=(6, 6))
    data['dir'] = data['dir'].astype(float)
    data['speed'] = data['speed'].astype(float)
    sns.scatterplot(x='dir', y='speed', data=data)
    plt.title('What is the relationship between wind speed and wind direction?', wrap=True)
    plt.xlabel('Wind Direction')
    plt.ylabel('Wind Speed (m/s)')
    plt.xticks(rotation=45)
    if len(plt.xticks()[0]) > 20:
        plt.gca().xaxis.set_major_locator(ticker.MaxNLocator(20))
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import seaborn as sns
import matplotlib.ticker as ticker
def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    plt.figure(figsize=(6, 6))
    sns.histplot(data=data, x='dir', bins=36)
    plt.title('What is the distribution of wind direction?', wrap=True)
    plt.xlabel('Wind direction')
    plt.ylabel('Frequency')
    plt.xticks(rotation=45)
    if len(plt.xticks()[0]) > 20:
        plt.gca().xaxis.set_major_locator(ticker.MaxNLocator(20))
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import seaborn as sns
import matplotlib.ticker as ticker
def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    plt.figure(figsize=(6, 6))
    data['longitude'] = pd.to_numeric(data['longitude'])
    data['latitude'] = pd.to_numeric(data['latitude'])
    sns.kdeplot(data=data, x='longitude', y='latitude', fill=True, cmap='coolwarm', levels=20, thresh=0.05)
    plt.xlabel('Longitude')
    plt.ylabel('Latitude')
    plt.xticks(rotation=45)
    if len(plt.xticks()[0]) > 20:
        plt.gca().xaxis.set_major_locator(ticker.MaxNLocator(20))
    plt.title('What is the spatial distribution of wind vectors?', wrap=True)
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)
